high_descs: Walk towards the dishwasher in front of you.
Pick up the spoon to the right of the plate on the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the sink on your left.
Place the spoon in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn right and open the drawer with the fork already in it.
Place the spoon in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon in a drawer with the fork.

high_descs: Turn right, pass refrigerator, walk to counter.
Turn right, walk to sink, turn left to face sink.
Put spoon in sink, fill sink with water, empty sink.
Turn right, walk to drawer, put spoon in drawer.
anns.task_desc: Wash spoon, put it in drawer.

high_descs: Move forward to the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Clean the spoon in the sink with water.
Bring the spoon to the drawer right of the sink.
Put the spoon in the drawer right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon in the drawer right of the sink.
